            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國利郎(01234)公布，今年首季「LILANZ」產品零售額，較去年同期錄得低雙位數增長。</p>\n</div>",
