            "title": "保利置業上月合同銷售按年降逾13% 首季則跌逾22%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">保利置業(00119)公布，在今年3月份實現合同銷售約52億元(人民幣．下同)，較去年同期的60億元少13.33%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：保利置業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20240604_FI_source-web_00119.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：保利置業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20240604_FI_source-web_00119.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：保利置業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">期內銷售涉及樓面約17.5萬平方米，均價每平方米2.97萬元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">若將今年首3個月合計，該公司季度合同銷售約112億元，較去年同期的145億元少22.76%；涉及樓面39.6萬平方米，均價每平方米2.82萬元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15848079-%e4%bf%9d%e5%88%a9%e7%bd%ae%e6%a5%ad%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%88%e5%90%88%e5%90%8c%e9%8a%b7%e5%94%ae%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e9%99%8d%e9%80%be13-%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e5%89%87%e8%b7%8c%e9%80%be22",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508029_FI_source-web_00119.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-08 16:50:28",
